{"tid":237060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【西九關公】要求西九澄清 被搬上枱雪糕店喊冤 : 對我好唔公平","createTime":"2017-05-10T06:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T06:52:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf530b0af77085c398cecdb23ac794c4e3df8afb","tid":237060,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"西九龍中心昨日在Facebook上載8樓另一雪糕店老闆黃生早前受訪報導，由於行為未有得到黃生的同意，他得知事件後，立即要求西九將報導下架：「我今早親身去找西九龍有關人士問清楚，他們已即時删Post。」<br />\n<br />\n對於另一快將結業雪糕店的新聞，黃生表示對方指被其他雪糕店投訴，此事對他不公平：「我沒有投訴過他們，他們應該要拿出證據，否則會影響同層的雪糕店。」<br />\n<br />\n問到有沒有被網民滋擾？黃生直言：「有，今日有人經過我店外時，對著我的店説垃圾。」<br />\n<br />\n事件演變至今，黃生希望西九龍中心可出來澄清，交代拒續租原因，免令其他同行蒙冤。"},{"pid":"b324caa494f8cfe8aa24217f29aadd536c996279","tid":237060,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"陰公，比西九擺上臺同人吸傷"},{"pid":"901cdf7b9d512d091a7582212297fd7b00059b7c","tid":237060,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"好可憐"},{"pid":"46d0825ae55d9b335f76b21537cc6c539b03bff1","tid":237060,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170509/508956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170509%2F508956&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9da3f726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170509%2F508956&h=9e527e55\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170509/508956</a>"},{"pid":"56e77f652053dfe3c7bc837075b0b4907e479ea9","tid":237060,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"可能西九係想一次收曬兩間雪糕店皮,反正兩間都係賣咁平<br />\n<br />\n換haagen dazs收貴租好多"},{"pid":"c860828dc3213158d53227b96493ff44b9f9769a","tid":237060,"uid":49499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re